title: Red Rat - Monsters Of Dancehall
description:
Wallace Wilson, better known by his stage name Red Rat, is a Jamaican dancehall reggae recording and performing artist. He was born January 17, 1978 in St. Anns Bay, Jamaica. He is known for his up-beat music, comical style, and signature catch phrase "Oh No!"
